title: Phatu Kat
overview: Napa had a miscarriage when her husband was abroad on a mission, she was desperate to find a replacement to cover it. Lampao, the housemaid of Napa, was pregnant of a twin and agreed with Napa to give her one of her babies as she received news from a fortune teller that they would try to kill each other if kept together. Lampao decided to give Sasin to her and move out as far away as possible together with Ravit. The twins however meet each other 22 years later without knowing their relationship when they are both studying at the same Air Force Acadamy, in which they both are competing for a young beautiful girl named Arpaluck...
